button_counter_offer.componentleveltooltip: Counteroffer||Discard the proposed deal and construct a new one.

localised_text.tooltip_text: Balance offer||Automatically add a payment to get a balanced deal. This will not change any items that are already proposed, including payments.
Propose offer||Propose the above deal. You can only propose an offer if the recipient has a positive opinion about it.
Threaten||Threaten the recipient in an attempt to force the deal. This will result in war if rejected. Threatening counts as an act of treachery, reducing your reliability rating.
War coordination||Coordinate military efforts with your allies or vassals.
